Text.Page: Supplies arrived from the federation to help you defeat the archdevan army.

,

The archdevan threat we've seen surging is far from over, and we should prepare for another battle.

I have new supplies from the federation that might help.

Come find me in Highwatch when you're ready.

Nice to see you agan, !

I have new armor for you from the federation's best smiths. You can never go wrong with fresh gear. Good luck out there.
